      *@        명목액기준잔액
               MOVE  RJL0125-CRNCY-BAL
                 TO  RJL0125-TTL-AMT-BASE-BAL

170224*@       BS기준한도 = 통화한도
               MOVE  RJL0125-CRNCY-CLAM
                 TO  RJL0125-BS-BASE-CLAM

           ELSE
      *@통화별　원화환산금액 CALCURATER
